{{item:3151}}  The only complaint I would have with this post is the idea that Radagast is _supposed_ to be eccentric and bumbling. They may have portrayed him that way in the hobbit film but its a far cry from how the character seemed to exist in the **book** universe (Both Unfinished Tales, and the Lotr trilogy.) {{item:3151}}
